Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.10,0:00:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要哭？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.89,0:00:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.46,0:00:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.16,0:00:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样看起来岂不像是我在单方面地欺负后辈吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.48,0:00:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想哭的是我才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.60,0:00:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但被妹妹敬而远之 而且连个理由都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.30,0:00:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不对我诉说呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.46,0:00:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你来说我就只是这种程度的人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.90,0:00:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 成为姐妹又有什么意义呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.30,0:00:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要接受念珠呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.63,0:00:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.90,0:00:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另找一天心平气和地再谈谈吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.28,0:00:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也稍微有点过于激动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.71,0:01:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能说得也太过份了一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.11,0:01:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.39,0:01:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？ 佑巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.22,0:01:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.93,0:01:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始商议明天活动吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.37,0:01:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.37,0:01:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.27,0:01:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也想单方面地将我当成坏人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.85,0:01:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.19,0:01:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.18,0:01:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集在玛莉亚的庭院里的少女们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.81,0:01:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也带着天使般无垢的笑容 穿越与身同高的门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.18,0:01:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覆盖住纯洁身心的是深色的制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.79,0:01:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要让裙子的摺痕乱掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.67,0:02:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要让白色的水手服领结外翻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.81,0:02:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒缓的行走成了这里的习俗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.71,0:02:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私立莉莉安女学园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.32,0:02:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是少女的花园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.37,0:03:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)}吃惊的巧克力·后篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.24,0:03:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红蔷薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.20,0:03:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是四季常开呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.45,0:04:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概被姐姐讨厌了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.14,0:04:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.84,0:04:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.45,0:04:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我想你或许愿意自已一个人待着 但…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.73,0:04:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过说起来 刚才真像是过去情景的重现啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.93,0:04:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.03,0:04:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑巳与祥子有时真是相似得让人吃惊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.10,0:04:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的佑巳与祥子\N就像是一年又十个月以前的祥子与蓉子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.59,0:04:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是现在的红蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.51,0:04:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子因为成长环境的原因 所以不大擅长表达自已的意见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.23,0:05:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常因闷得慌而发脾气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.43,0:05:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是祥子大人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.06,0:05:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以某一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.43,0:05:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓉子对她训斥道“你这样我什么都无法明白”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.86,0:05:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“有想说的话就清楚地说出来”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.59,0:05:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不说话？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.92,0:05:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你内心深处的话语为什么就不能向我倾诉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.28,0:05:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话我什么都无法明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.68,0:05:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被蓉子那样训斥后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.61,0:05:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子也像是忍耐到了极限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.19,0:05:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后就渐渐变得能表达自已的意见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.60,0:05:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 这大概就是祥子对佑巳感到焦躁不安的原因吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.30,0:05:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焦躁不安？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.55,0:05:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.74,0:05:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.65,0:05:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.05,0:05:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为看到佑巳就像是看到了自已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.69,0:05:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子她的本性并未改变啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.71,0:05:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也一定是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.99,0:05:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才焦躁不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.37,0:06:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在佑巳的身上\N看到了自已身上也有的讨厌部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.53,0:06:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以原谅祥子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.75,0:06:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原谅什么的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.84,0:06:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 不要因为这点事就变得讨厌祥子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.48,0:06:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.97,0:06:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.68,0:06:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对这个温室 稍微有点过敏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.62,0:06:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.07,0:06:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白蔷薇大人很快就要毕业了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.82,0:06:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后我该怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.15,0:06:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再没有能像这样来帮助我的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.57,0:06:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是说了些让人开心的话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.92,0:06:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总会有办法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.14,0:06:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能再多向祥子诉说一些真心话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.43,0:06:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衹要至少能做到一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.77,0:06:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管发生什么事一定都能顺利地渡过的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.38,0:07:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.80,0:07:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 向佑巳布置一道作业题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.93,0:07:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭自已的力量与祥子重归于好 好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.56,0:07:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.63,0:07:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～ 佑巳不送我巧克力吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.34,0:07:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向志摩子同学说声“给我巧克力”不就好了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.58,0:07:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.65,0:07:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么只有放弃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.06,0:07:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.08,0:07:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不给我巧克力的话 我就吃掉佑巳喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.16,0:07:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边是祥子大人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.57,0:07:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失败品就留作用情不专的白蔷薇大人的惩罚用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.96,0:07:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是情人节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.13,0:07:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先必须对昨天的事道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.68,0:07:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 将祥子大人叫出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.11,0:08:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.79,0:08:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是佑巳同学啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.99,0:08:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志摩子同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.28,0:08:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人来了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.70,0:08:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 在上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.22,0:08:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.85,0:08:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.69,0:08:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.79,0:08:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志摩子同学也许把卡片藏在这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.97,0:08:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再胡闹了 由乃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.59,0:08:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不告诉我卡片藏在哪里也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.04,0:08:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只听一下我的预测好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.03,0:08:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 来得正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.71,0:08:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 能否把这个吵人家伙带出去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.08,0:08:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.41,0:08:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐是小气鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.22,0:08:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.56,0:08:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑巳同学 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.98,0:09:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃同学 请稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.22,0:09:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.70,0:09:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.67,0:09:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 昨天真是对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.09,0:09:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 如果方便的话 今天能给我一点时间吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.78,0:09:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想继续昨天的话题吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.80,0:09:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.81,0:09:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻宝结束后如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.67,0:09:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我在温室等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.53,0:09:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温室？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.18,0:09:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 那么就在温室见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.36,0:09:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢大家的勇跃参加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.73,0:09:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我说明一下活动规则
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.00,0:09:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要找的就是这些卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.85,0:09:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红 白 黄的卡片将分别藏在校内的某处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.14,0:09:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限制时间是一小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.16,0:10:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到卡片后 请带回到作为本部的蔷薇馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.28,0:10:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着就可获赠\N作为附加奖的与花蕾们的半天约会权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.06,0:10:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受欢迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.18,0:10:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.38,0:10:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 请花蕾的姐妹们到前面来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.70,0:10:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了公平起见 请花蕾的姐妹们迟五分钟开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.11,0:10:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！ 怎么这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.31,0:10:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 开始！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.88,0:10:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在活动结束前 花蕾们请来这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.65,0:10:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到黄蔷薇大人竟然也会参加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.24,0:10:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没理由白白放过这么有趣的活动吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.26,0:10:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我一定会找到红色的卡片的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.53,0:10:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 稍微招呼一下客人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.32,0:10:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 方便的话能否进来谈谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.29,0:11:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有花蕾们在哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.76,0:11:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白蔷薇大人不想去找志摩子同学的卡片吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.17,0:11:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你说是志摩子的卡片…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.86,0:11:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 关于隐藏的地点我是一点头绪也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.82,0:11:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 明明志摩子同学的卡片大概就在那里的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.78,0:11:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.60,0:11:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说那个房间里藏着什么好东西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.39,0:11:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.75,0:11:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 已过了5分钟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.81,0:11:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请大家开始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.05,0:11:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.52,0:11:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待着佑巳的英勇奋斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.74,0:11:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.46,0:11:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑巳同学 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.41,0:11:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.31,0:11:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕啊 志摩子同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.38,0:11:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以跟白蔷薇大人约会啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.88,0:11:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人既没参加什么俱乐部活动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.00,0:11:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没加入什么委员会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.41,0:12:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.17,0:12:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是在蔷薇馆里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.96,0:12:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.18,0:12:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.15,0:12:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.04,0:12:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是祥子大人的FAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.64,0:12:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概以为我知道卡片藏在哪里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.50,0:12:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.24,0:12:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～ 现在可不是玩捉迷藏的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.65,0:12:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～ 还有十五分钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.05,0:12:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人的红色卡片到底在哪里呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.10,0:12:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我要藏的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.03,0:12:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.47,0:13:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我的话 一定会藏在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.41,0:13:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.77,0:13:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 好像吓到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.00,0:13:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.56,0:13:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是来这里找卡片吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.02,0:13:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.52,0:13:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人 比我更早来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.93,0:13:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 看起来还未找到卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.60,0:13:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.45,0:13:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.13,0:13:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想卡片应该就在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.52,0:13:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便的话 请用这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.42,0:13:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.73,0:13:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那里没有卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.21,0:13:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.46,0:13:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我说晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.72,0:14:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上我刚才也挖掘过那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.56,0:14:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.26,0:14:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会认为卡片在那里呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.35,0:14:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.53,0:14:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这个蔷薇就叫做红蔷薇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.72,0:14:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经到4点40分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.00,0:14:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加活动的同学们请立刻到中庭集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.21,0:14:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 我们将发表本次活动的结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.86,0:14:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花蕾们的卡片有两张被发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.43,0:14:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 没找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.64,0:14:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为令不给我提示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.86,0:14:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.32,0:14:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐的卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.79,0:14:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为一定会在那里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.97,0:14:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是找到白色卡片的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.66,0:14:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年级藤组 蟹名静同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.75,0:15:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～ 是静啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.39,0:15:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明用表情给过提示的 这个人真是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.70,0:15:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到白色卡片的地点是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.63,0:15:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委员会的公告牌上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.43,0:15:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 不在蔷薇馆的第一层吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.28,0:15:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么志摩子同学为什么那时会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.26,0:15:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着 是找到黄色卡片的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.66,0:15:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年级菊组 田沼千里同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.06,0:15:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地点是在图书馆里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.29,0:15:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,图书馆我也去找过啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.97,0:15:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.10,0:15:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红蔷薇的花蕾的卡片谁也没发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.85,0:15:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也没有？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.99,0:15:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红蔷薇的花蕾 红色卡片究竟在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.79,0:15:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 一起去收回卡片吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.90,0:15:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.49,0:16:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来过这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.05,0:16:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 却没有找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.83,0:16:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找了哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.70,0:16:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在红蔷薇根茎的附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.19,0:16:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.53,0:16:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的找了这里吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.78,0:16:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.89,0:16:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.94,0:16:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.61,0:16:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明挖掘过同一个地方的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.86,0:16:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑巳同学 虽然很遗憾…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.66,0:16:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没说谎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.19,0:16:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有证人在场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.45,0:16:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.48,0:16:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是… 不认识的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.33,0:16:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就没法成为证人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.01,0:16:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.91,0:16:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.34,0:16:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都说到这种地步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.70,0:16:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才是真的不在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.30,0:16:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.52,0:17:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 这张卡片放在了比我原来埋得更深的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.37,0:17:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.00,0:17:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.20,0:17:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣瓦伦丁做了一个恶作剧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.64,0:17:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样去想不是很好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.13,0:17:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然红蔷薇的花蕾都这样说了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.90,0:17:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.91,0:17:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 能在蔷薇馆等我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.17,0:17:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.70,0:17:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志摩子同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.22,0:17:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.51,0:17:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哦 佑巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.24,0:17:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我特意等在这里为你送的巧克力说声谢谢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.01,0:17:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.48,0:18:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力的话这里有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.27,0:18:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是非常难吃的夹心巧克力就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.98,0:18:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.22,0:18:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 放在那里的巧克力不是佑巳的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.28,0:18:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.31,0:18:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 我已经吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.30,0:18:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为佑巳紧盯着那扇门 所以我完全以为…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.46,0:18:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是非常美味的大理石花纹蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.16,0:18:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过好像是初学者做的 样子稍微有点变形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.31,0:18:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 那是粉红色的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.94,0:18:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 粉红色的包装纸上印着白色蔷薇花纹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.25,0:18:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在蔷薇馆第一层里藏的不是白色卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.75,0:18:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是志摩子同学因为犹豫着该不该交给\N白蔷薇大人而一直放在那里的巧克力蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.68,0:18:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也算圣瓦伦丁的一个恶作剧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.95,0:19:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.14,0:19:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.64,0:19:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有东西希望你能收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.47,0:19:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道… 不会是念珠吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.40,0:19:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,念珠！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.66,0:19:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.20,0:19:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.19,0:19:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我一年级的时候 好像是被姐姐完全看穿了似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.62,0:19:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我对你的心事却不怎么了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.95,0:19:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以渐渐变得没有自信了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.39,0:19:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.77,0:19:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 看起来你好像在避开我 所以稍微有点急躁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.96,0:19:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那是我的误解吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.37,0:19:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 那是因为我想把这个送给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.48,0:19:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在令大人的帮助下做出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.14,0:19:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为想先对姐姐保密 才会偷偷摸摸地去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.23,0:20:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人在那里沾沾自喜地做得起劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.29,0:20:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却完全没有想到姐姐会怎么想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.40,0:20:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.03,0:20:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的 姐姐讨厌情人节的巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.45,0:20:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我无论如何也想将\N平常那种感谢的心情化为有形的物质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.67,0:20:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.45,0:20:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.27,0:20:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过讨厌什么的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.80,0:20:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所厌烦的只是一部份学生随便地\N将送巧克力的欲望想放在我身上实现而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.41,0:20:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你为我做的东西的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.89,0:20:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会很高兴地收下它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.37,0:20:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能给我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.24,0:20:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.29,0:20:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说了我不是讨厌巧克力…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.36,0:20:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一个不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.79,0:20:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 请拿这边的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.51,0:20:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人请放手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.74,0:20:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑巳你才应该…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.64,0:21:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.17,0:21:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 又是在做什么表演吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.86,0:21:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的 这叫做“吃惊的巧克力”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.92,0:21:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里面混入了难吃得让人歪嘴的“不中”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.89,0:21:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才叫“吃惊”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.04,0:21:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.05,0:21:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.61,0:21:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.95,0:21:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.40,0:21:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么那就是“中”了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.17,0:21:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明“中”与“不中”都有一个不见了的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.10,0:21:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人会吃到“中”也算是圣瓦伦丁的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.77,0:21:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃到“中”会有什么好事吗？
